T1  - Investment in new activities and the welfare cost of uncertainty
AU  - Aizenman, Joshua
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 52
IS  - 2
SP  - 259
EP  - 277
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/04/01/
SN  - 0304-3878
